# This file exists only so that `backend/migrations/` is committed and
# present at Docker build time (the `backend/Dockerfile` builder stage
# performs a `COPY migrations ./migrations` that requires the directory
# to exist on the host). Track 1 / Group 1 will populate this directory
# with the three node-pg-migrate forward+reverse files specified in
# AAP §0.6.3 (ST-031, ST-030, ST-035 — every filename must embed its
# story ID per Rule R10).
